{"tid":2488561,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）廢青樓淡寫大字控訴：要求阿媽賣樓分300萬","createTime":"2021-04-14T10:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T11:43:32.000Z","uid":361751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"581529ee5ae25f83eb8a8cf5a1acbd39bdc2d4b4","tid":2488561,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報：<br />\n<br />\n我為樓狂｜網傳兒子控訴 要求阿媽賣樓分300萬 疾呼「我要嘅係尊重」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfAXC5Rd4EHLnsadDrKpAVq3WmtGmJVJtrG2dH91ERqFW?filename=2oeUXD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oeUXD3.png&h=d0ff99e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情下本港樓價仍高企，家有黃金屋雖可維繫關係，相反，亦能成為分家的原因。最近網上流傳一輯圖片，疑似有兒子要求阿媽賣樓分身家，更大咬要分300萬元，疑索價不果，將全屋家具推倒慘變成「廢墟」，並要報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWUGzEretma8EhHEyTV6DRPaUtvxtC6UbJN2UMUsxQn3T?filename=Ser8hEc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSer8hEc.png&h=321c2b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一輯照片，疑似一名兒子為強逼母親賣樓欲分300萬元樓價，而將單位搗亂成廢墟。(資料來源:facebook《今日有野講》)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUNYfZDo2ruvRbGkDoJKtEtUiuio14oL6Dw8hLzkajuxa?filename=xEqAG53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxEqAG53.png&h=ea1cf563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該名搗亂的子女在牆上寫下大字報，要求母親賣樓，並分單位一半價錢。(資料來源:facebook《今日有野講》)"},{"pid":"d8ab7f40ec18ad05fc78f85b7b29e97976f3683c","tid":2488561,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVopWXAEfnmgmX3bLKF3aPGb6xnmmzFJj1Efh5qUhMKk5?filename=gUAMOMN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUAMOMN.png&h=1ff7da98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫明要求分到300萬元，並提供4萬元生活費。(資料來源:facebook《今日有野講》)"},{"pid":"c9e6a022496636c156be5f0f5d1fa5ff44ac7b59","tid":2488561,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"網絡平台Facebook《今日有野講》流傳一輯照片，指有人「要阿媽賣樓分錢唔成拆屋泄憤」，照片可見，一個住宅單位客廳至睡房均被人搗亂，客廳雜物散落一地，十分凌亂，梳化、抽屜、地面均滿佈家中物品。電視機及枱燈被人推倒在地上。<br />\n<br />\n牆身更寫上大字：「To 老媽，我想你應該還不是很明白。我不是在外住到6月份。我係要分一半房屋的價錢，3百萬。之後過我自己的生活。我不會回來的了。」又言：「我要嘅係尊重，對自由、尊嚴、平等嘅待遇。自己的私生活、工作都與你和任何人無關。」房門亦大大隻字寫上「賣樓」。圖中可見，有警員接報到場。不過，事件發生具體時間及地點不詳。"},{"pid":"588fdd32f83cc4a09d4fcffb63a76653d798ba0b","tid":2488561,"uid":362300,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"係咪韓林兒黎"},{"pid":"8455234be2c61876f94f410f438ff00cbc3578d3","tid":2488561,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"588fdd32f83cc4a09d4fcffb63a76653d798ba0b","tid":2488561,"uid":362300,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"係咪韓林兒黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來係迫老母賣"},{"pid":"4e786c65c96ac7677b5f8ccce36039d49a08c943","tid":2488561,"uid":74927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"有冇份供先 層樓本身係父母買落既話<br />\n個仔憑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a246cbfd41d8137867091df32c11025cc7e6e1","tid":2488561,"uid":176401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"呢d癈人 俾幾球佢幾年洗L曬又會返黎嘈住要養埋佢 因為老竇老母生佢出黎要負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db256447247cc8314e729a0e3331d327a790ed75","tid":2488561,"uid":65928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老鳳要留資產比你？"},{"pid":"102ad11e5a020e1fcc410dbfcb24d92ebacc3ea9","tid":2488561,"uid":45783,"like":0,"dislike":